    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that won't break the bank? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready to hit the road! It shows some honest wear and tear from its years of service, but it remains a solid, functional choice for anyone looking for reliable transportation with plenty of life left. It's the perfect balance of affordability and utility for your everyday needs!",
