    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to offer this superlative vehicle, currently presented in showroom condition. Having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection, this motorcar remains in an unblemished state, both mechanically and aesthetically. It represents a rare opportunity for the sophisticated buyer to acquire a specimen of peerless quality and meticulously preserved history. This is, without reservation, the finest example available on the market today.",
