    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it looks and smells just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I've totally babied it since day one, keeping it garaged and spotless. It drives like a absolute dream and is ready for your next big road trip. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed! Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
