      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a superlative example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in a state of unblemished excellence, mirroring its original showroom delivery standards. Meticulously curated and maintained to the most exacting specifications, every surface\u2014from the pristine interior appointments to the flawless exterior finish\u2014reflects a commitment to mechanical and aesthetic integrity. This is an investment-grade opportunity for the discerning collector who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
